1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,740
The message for the bedside: recognize early

2
00:00:02,740 --> 00:00:04,697
with troponin and cardiac MRI.

3
00:00:04,697 --> 00:00:06,263
Admit for rhythm monitoring.

4
00:00:06,263 --> 00:00:09,003
Restrict exertion for three to six months.

5
00:00:09,003 --> 00:00:11,743
And escalate to immunosuppression or mechanical support

6
00:00:11,743 --> 00:00:13,700
when the phenotype demands it.
